I can specify what could be in the footer and then add it in to my actual app later on.

00:17:48.500 --> 00:17:55.500
Within the layout of BS Lib, I can specify the theme and customize how I want my app to look.

00:17:55.500 --> 00:17:59.500
So in this case, I'm saying I want the Cosmo boot swatch theme.

00:17:59.500 --> 00:18:05.500
I want a white background, this color foreground, this font, et cetera.

00:18:05.500 --> 00:18:09.500
